data.description: Charming residence with abundant character and an abundance of windows for savoring scenic vistas. Relish moments of relaxation on the rear deck while taking in the sunrise. The spacious living room features a lovely native stone fireplace with a temperature-controlled pellet insert and in-floor heating. Additionally, there's a one-car garage and workshop, as well as an office or hobby room. This delightful home is nestled in a quaint small community within easy reach of restaurants and nightlife.
